Installation: http://wiki.ros.org/noetic/Installation/Ubuntu
video -> https://youtu.be/PowY8dV36DY

In every bash terminal source the script
echo "source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash" >> ~/.bashrc  --> adds the line at last of .bashrc
source ~/.bashrc

sudo apt install ros-noetic-joint-state-publisher <-- dependency

